       </para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
       <para>
        In <application>psql</>, no longer print an empty line for
        unaligned, expanded output for zero rows (Peter Eisentraut)
       </para>
      </listitem>

     </itemizedlist>

    </sect5>

